text:
Queens Boulevard, north side, at 62nd Drive, showing four views of the Horst (white) house of 1896. Beyond it is a pumping station for this area. At the left is seen in view three, the rear of the Covert house. In the center background is the Thompson house and barn. Note also the filling in and widening in views 3 and 4.

April 1923
View 2: February 8, 1924
View 3: February 1924
View 4: March 1925.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
